RISE & SHINE
Please fill out this card to place your breakfast order and hand it to your flight
attendant before settling in for the night.
Breakfast will be served with your choice of beverage approximately 75 minutes prior to arrival.
Should you prefer to eat prior to this, please inform your flight attendant.
Would you like to be woken up for breakfast?
AYes O No
I will not be having breakfast

votre petit-déjeuner avant de vous préparer pour dormir.
